<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />You covered the earth with water like a garment;</para>

<para style="q1">the water covered the mountains.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />Your rebuke made the waters recede;</para>

<para style="q1">at the sound of your thunderous voice they fled.</para>
